<p>Besides economic links, the Bay of Bengal countries share a cultural and civilisational legacy. Therefore, institutions lik<strong>e Nalanda University</strong> can play a role in promoting research on cultural and civilisational linkage.</p>
<p>BIMSTEC is not reinventing the wheel, but it is&nbsp;<strong>rediscovering common heritage around BoB.</strong></p>